{"type": "article", "id": 12383, "title": "北欧极简风格的突破", "description": "", "date": "2015-07-21T07:42:29Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 22, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607122511xPOW5CQERqhz6Ks3.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t哥本哈根设计师 Ellinor Ericsson 耿耿于怀与北欧设计的极简，这种极简主义甚至被人诟病为乏味无趣。于是 Ellinor Ericsson 试图在简单的设计的基础上加入一些有趣的装饰，她试图把洛可可风格和北欧风格结合在一起，在简单的桦木椅子上编织上五彩的十字扣，结构和材料是北欧式的，而颜色和装饰形状是洛可可式的，让简单的设计也变得好玩儿一点。这里是<a href=\"http://www.ellinorericsson.com/\" target=\"_blank\">设计师的个人主页</a>，点击可以查看更多作品。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140126mwYNVGiabjZWzJTv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140127UtVhLFyxPrDB8MJi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140127an3WwTm45ZfMxHUR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140128Ms3Pv9pZmBbJioaE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140128rRBeLXPWCxF2juy3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140129iAXRlcTu2YL8P695.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140129mGNwb9SFfnrXayC4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140130Hpqs8gtQeuh2ETmX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n\n"}